{"actor":"G. H. Chinoy","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-12T18:29:08Z","event_type":"updated","id":192,"issue_id":"riptide-fiz","new_value":"{\"description\":\"The implementation of the c7z epic missed critical architectural constraints. 1) cmd/session-viewer/main_test.go asserts a 404 for missing routes, but it MUST assert a 200 OK serving index.html to support SPA routing. 2) pkg/tui/tui_test.go needs tests for the 'l' and 'h' toggles, and must verify that consecutive EventThinking messages append to a list rather than overwriting.\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"riptide-fiz\",\"title\":\"Fix missing test constraints from c7z epic (SPA Fallback \\u0026 TUI Observability)\",\"description\":\"The implementation of the c7z epic missed critical architectural constraints. 1)  asserts a 404 for missing routes, but it MUST assert a 200 OK serving  to support SPA routing. 2)  needs tests for the 'l' and 'h' toggles, and must verify that consecutive  messages append to a list rather than overwriting.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"ghchinoy@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T00:28:57Z\",\"created_by\":\"G. H. Chinoy\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T00:28:57Z\"}"}
